00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:24,560
A false positive is where the IDS system tells us that it is an attack, but in fact it is

23
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,560
not.

24
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:32,160
And that would actually require the organization to launch into its incident response capability

