33
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:18,120
And we've talked about how it's important to fine tune your IDS IPS capabilities so that

34
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:26,320
we lower, for example, the false positives, but we also try and raise the false negatives.

35
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:33,800
I mean, we want the IDS IPS system to be as valuable as possible so that it catches everything.

36
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:40,800
And that requires constant fine tuning so that it returns better decisions on an ongoing

37
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,160
basis.

