00:03:55,400 --> 00:04:01,080
And if you know anything about these, these are fake environments that companies create

42
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:07,200
to look very attractive so that if an intruder has intruded into your network, you lure

43
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:11,440
them into these fake environments because they look attractive.

44
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:17,160
But because they are fake, they can lure these people into those environments so that you

45
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,800
can protect your real environments.

